This script can be used to download youtube videos[singles and playlists] or just as MP3. Apart from that you can also directly download the SecTalks indexed here https://github.com/PaulSec/awesome-sec-talks

Usage: massSecVidDl.py [-h] [-l LINK] [-p PLAYLIST] [-s]

Youtube video download tool

optional arguments:
  -h, --help               Show this help message and exit
  -l LINK, --link LINK     Single youtube video to download
  -p PLAYLIST, --playlist  PLAYLIST
                           Youtube playlist url to download all videos
  -s, --sec                All sec-talk videos
  -m, --mp3                Download as MP3

